The tested build is stored in a secure repository. 

Real- World Example: 

	1. Docker image is stored in 
		a. ECR (Elastic Container Registry) - AWS
		b. GCR ( Google Container Registry) - GCP 
		c. ACR (Azure Container Registry) - Azure 
	2. JAR/WAR files stored in Jfrog Artifactory.
	3. Helm charts stored in ChartMuseum

Artifacts ensure repeatable deployments. 

